Member UE Selection Assistance Subscriptions (Collection)

Retrieve all the active Member UE Selection Assistance Subscriptions managed by the NEF.

Authorizations:
NoneoAuth2ClientCredentials
path Parameters
afId
required
string

Represents the identifier of the AF

Responses

/{apiRoot}/3gpp-musa/v1/{afId}/subscriptions

Create a new Member UE Selection Assistance Subscription.

Authorizations:
NoneoAuth2ClientCredentials
path Parameters
afId
required
string

Represents the identifier of the AF

Request Body schema: application/json
required
One of
afId
string

Represents the identifier of the AF.

tgtUeIds
required
Array of strings (Gpsi) non-empty [ items^(msisdn-[0-9]{5,15}|extid-[^@]+@[^@]+|.+)$ ]

Contains the list of identifier(s) of the UEs for which Member UE Selection Assistance Reporting is requested.

Array of objects or objects or objects (IpAddr) non-empty

Contains the IP addresses of a list of UEs for Member UE Selection Assistance Reporting.

notifUri
required
string (Uri)

string providing an URI formatted according to IETF RFC 3986.

notifId
required
string

Contains the Notification Correlation ID assigned by the AF.

expTime
string <date-time> (DateTime)

string with format "date-time" as defined in OpenAPI.

Array of objects (QoSFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the QoS filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (AccessRatTypeFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the Access types and Rat types filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (E2ETransTimeFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the End-to-end data volume transfer time filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeLocFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the UE location filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeHisLocFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the UE historical location filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeDirectionFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the UE direction filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeDistanceFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the UE distance filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (ServiceExpFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the Service Experience filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (DnnFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the DNN filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

memUpdatePeriod
integer (schemas-DurationSec)

indicating a time in seconds.

maxUeNum
integer (Uinteger) >= 0

Unsigned Integer, i.e. only value 0 and integers above 0 are permissible.

object (TimeWindow)

Represents a time window identified by a start time and a stop time.

suppFeat
string (SupportedFeatures) ^[A-Fa-f0-9]*$

A string used to indicate the features supported by an API that is used as defined in clause 6.6 in 3GPP TS 29.500. The string shall contain a bitmask indicating supported features in hexadecimal representation Each character in the string shall take a value of "0" to "9", "a" to "f" or "A" to "F" and shall represent the support of 4 features as described in table 5.2.2-3. The most significant character representing the highest-numbered features shall appear first in the string, and the character representing features 1 to 4 shall appear last in the string. The list of features and their numbering (starting with 1) are defined separately for each API. If the string contains a lower number of characters than there are defined features for an API, all features that would be represented by characters that are not present in the string are not supported.

Responses

Callbacks

/{apiRoot}/3gpp-musa/v1/{afId}/subscriptions

  • Payload
Content type
application/json
{
  • "afId": "string",

    • "string"

afId
string

Represents the identifier of the AF.

tgtUeIds
required
Array of strings (Gpsi) non-empty [ items^(msisdn-[0-9]{5,15}|extid-[^@]+@[^@]+|.+)$ ]

Contains the list of identifier(s) of the UEs for which Member UE Selection Assistance Reporting is requested.

Array of objects or objects or objects (IpAddr) non-empty

Contains the IP addresses of a list of UEs for Member UE Selection Assistance Reporting.

notifUri
required
string (Uri)

string providing an URI formatted according to IETF RFC 3986.

notifId
required
string

Contains the Notification Correlation ID assigned by the AF.

expTime
string <date-time> (DateTime)

string with format "date-time" as defined in OpenAPI.

Array of objects (QoSFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the QoS filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (AccessRatTypeFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the Access types and Rat types filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (E2ETransTimeFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the End-to-end data volume transfer time filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeLocFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the UE location filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeHisLocFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the UE historical location filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeDirectionFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the UE direction filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeDistanceFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the UE distance filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (ServiceExpFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the Service Experience filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (DnnFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the DNN filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

memUpdatePeriod
integer (schemas-DurationSec)

indicating a time in seconds.

maxUeNum
integer (Uinteger) >= 0

Unsigned Integer, i.e. only value 0 and integers above 0 are permissible.

object (TimeWindow)

Represents a time window identified by a start time and a stop time.

suppFeat
string (SupportedFeatures) ^[A-Fa-f0-9]*$

A string used to indicate the features supported by an API that is used as defined in clause 6.6 in 3GPP TS 29.500. The string shall contain a bitmask indicating supported features in hexadecimal representation Each character in the string shall take a value of "0" to "9", "a" to "f" or "A" to "F" and shall represent the support of 4 features as described in table 5.2.2-3. The most significant character representing the highest-numbered features shall appear first in the string, and the character representing features 1 to 4 shall appear last in the string. The list of features and their numbering (starting with 1) are defined separately for each API. If the string contains a lower number of characters than there are defined features for an API, all features that would be represented by characters that are not present in the string are not supported.

Responses

/{apiRoot}/3gpp-musa/v1/{afId}/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}

Request the Modification of an existing Individual Member UE Selection Assistance Subscription resource.

Authorizations:
NoneoAuth2ClientCredentials
path Parameters
afId
required
string

Represents the identifier of the AF.

subscriptionId
required
string

Represents the identifier of the Individual Member UE Selection Assistance Subscription resource.

Request Body schema: application/merge-patch+json
required
notifUri
string (Uri)

string providing an URI formatted according to IETF RFC 3986.

notifId
string
expTime
string <date-time> (DateTime)

string with format "date-time" as defined in OpenAPI.

Array of objects (QoSFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the updatedQoS filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (AccessRatTypeFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the updated Access types and Rat types filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (E2ETransTimeFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the updated End-to-end data volume transfer time filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeLocFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the updated UE location filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeHisLocFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the updated UE historical location filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeDirectionFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the updated UE direction filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (UeDistanceFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the updated UE distance filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (ServiceExpFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the updated Service Experience filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

Array of objects (DnnFilterCriteria) non-empty

Contains the updated DNN filtering criteria for Member UE selection.

memUpdatePeriod
integer or null (DurationSecRm)

indicating a time in seconds with OpenAPI defined 'nullable: true' property.

maxUeNum
integer or null (UintegerRm) >= 0

Unsigned Integer, i.e. only value 0 and integers above 0 are permissible with the OpenAPI 'nullable: true' property.

object (TimeWindow)

Represents a time window identified by a start time and a stop time.

Responses

/{apiRoot}/3gpp-musa/v1/{afId}/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}
